FOWLKES v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [P. C. No. 75,

September Term, 1959.]

Decided April 18, 1960.

Before Brune, C. J., and Henderson, Hammond, Prescott and Horney, JJ.

Per Curiam.

For the reasons set forth in Judge Warnken’s opinion below and the added citation of Wilson v. Warden, 222 Md. 580, the application for leave to appeal is denied.
